snippet.title: IONCINEMA
snippet.description:
IONCINEMA.com is a media outlet featuring daily news, reviews and interviews in American indie, World Cinema, Documentary film & film festivals. Our motto: We heart subtitles!

If you’re into micro-budgeted films, films with subtitles or love film festivals, you’ll want to check out the latest trailers, teasers, clips and exclusive video interviews. This is the official Youtube channel for IONCINEMA.com. 

IONCINEMA.com was founded by Eric Lavallée - http://www.ioncinema.com/author/eric-lavallee

Subscribe to our channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/ioncinema?sub_confirmation=1
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ioncinema
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ioncinema
Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/ioncinema
